p is <em>Urgency XIX</em>, from 2006, which is estimated at =C2=A3120,000. =
It=E2=80=99s been three years since anything by Tillmans was auctioned for =
a price above $100,000, and five years since a handful of the artist=E2=80=
=99s abstract images sold for prices above $100,000, peaking at a little be=
